               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18341124-name-423" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18341124-name-423" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18341124-name-423" type="surname" value="GIDDINS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18341124-name-423" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES GIDDINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at Bed-font, and am a retailer of beer. I missed my boiler on the 9th of November—my wife had used it on the 6th, and placed it in a shed—there were the marks of some person having got over the, folding doors into the shed, and where they got out—I made inquiries, and found the boiler about two hundred yards off—this is it—I know the prisoner—he is here and there, wherever he can get a lodging.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
